    "date": "2012-05-29T20:20:45Z",
    "text": "Connecting Rural America Act - Amends the Rural Electrification Act of 1936 to include grants in the rural broadband loan program. Limits grants to not more than 50% of a project's development costs, with a waiver for up to 75% of such costs.\n\nProvides higher grant rates for communities that are small, remote, high poverty, and working with specified stakeholders.\n\nAuthorizes appropriations for the program."
